event.title: Alpha Domus Wine Tasting
event.description:
We are so excited to invite you to our Alpha Domus wine tasting on 3rd July...

Alpha Domus Winemaker Barry Riwai is flying up from the Hawkes Bay just for this special wine tasting at Morell.  Please join us for a wonderful evening enjoying beautiful award winning wines matched with some platters from the Morell Kitchen Team.

$35 at 6pm - please call Morell on 600 3259 or email us at bookings@morell.co.nz.  Spaces are limited so ensure your space now!
